### 1. Public endpoint - no token (expect 200)
GET http://127.0.0.1/api/public

### 2. Secured endpoint - no token (expect 403)
GET http://127.0.0.1/api/secured

### 3. Secured endpoint - valid user token (expect 200)
GET http://127.0.0.1/api/secured
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 4. Secured endpoint - expired token (expect 401)
GET http://127.0.0.1/api/secured
Authorization: Bearer {{expired_token}}

### 5. Secured endpoint - wrong issuer (expect 401)
GET http://127.0.0.1/api/secured
Authorization: Bearer {{wrong_iss_token}}

### 6. Secured endpoint - garbage token (expect 401)
GET http://127.0.0.1/api/secured
Authorization: Bearer garbage.token.here

### 7. Admin endpoint - user role (expect 403)
GET http://127.0.0.1/api/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### 8. Admin endpoint - admin role (expect 200)
GET http://127.0.0.1/api/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
